scene.message:
Yukino: Hey, again? What's{nl}
the deal with this big,{nl}
gaudy door?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Wasn't there a similar room{nl}
just now?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Somehow we never reach{nl}
the very top no matter how{nl}
long we go!{waitkey}Ayase's beat!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Damn it. I sense the{nl}
malice of that Michiko woman{nl}
everywhere I turn{waitkey}!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: This tower feels far{nl}
taller than it looks from{nl}
outside.{waitkey}Just my imagination?{waitkey}{ret}
